\c 18
\s Hezekia mambo waJudha
\p
\v 1 Zvino negore rechitatu raHoshea mwanakomana waEra mambo waIsraeri, Hezekia mwanakomana waAhazi mambo waJudha wakatanga kubata ushe.
\v 2 Akatanga kubata ushe ava namakore ana makumi maviri namashanu; akabata ushe paJerusarema makore makumi maviri namapfumbamwe; zita ramai vake rakange riri Abhi mukunda waZekariya.
\v 3 Akaita zvakarurama pamberi paJehovha, sezvakaita baba vake Dhavhidhi.
\v 4 Akabvisa matunhu akakwirira, akaputsa shongwe, akaparadza matanda okunamata nawo; akaputsaputsa nyoka yendarira yakange yakaitwa naMozisi; nekuti kusvikira pamazuva iwayo vana vaIsraeri vaiipisira zvinonhuhwira; akaitumidza Nehushitani.
\v 5 Akatenda kuna Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri; naizvozvo hakuna wakange akafanana naye pakati pamadzimambo ose aJudha, kuna vakamutevera kana akamutangira.
\v 6 Nekuti wakanamatira Jehovha, haana kutsauka pakumutevera; asi wakachengeta mirairo yake, yakarairwa Mozisi naJehovha.
\v 7 Jehovha akava naye; kose kwaakaenda wakafambiswa zvakanaka; akamukira mambo weAsiriya, akasamushumira.
\v 8 Akakunda vaFirisitia kusvikira paGaza nenyika yaro, kubva pachirindo chomurindi kusvikira pamaguta akakombwa norusvingo.
\v 9 Zvino negore rechina ramambo Hezekia, riri gore rechinomwe raHoshea mwanakomana waEra mambo waIsraeri, Sharimaneseri mambo weAsiriya akanorwa neSamaria, akarikomba.
\v 10 Pakupera kwamakore matatu vakarikunda; Samaria rikakundwa negore retanhatu raHezekia, riri gore repfumbamwe raHoshea mambo waIsraeri.
\v 11 Mambo weAsiriya akatapa vaIsraeri, akaenda navo Asiriya, akavaisa paHara, napaHabhori, parwizi Gozani, nomumaguta avaMedhi;
\v 12 nekuti havana kuteerera inzwi raJehovha Mwari wavo, asi vakadarika sungano yake, izvo zvose zvavakange varairwa naMozisi muranda waJehovha, vakaramba kunzwa, kana kuzviita.
\s Saniheribhi mambo weAsiriya anokomba Jerusarema, asi vaJudha vanorwirwa naJehovha
\p
\v 13 Zvino negore regumi namana ramambo Hezekia, Saniheribhi mambo weAsiriya akanorwa namaguta ose aJudha akakombwa namasvingo, akaakunda.
\v 14 Zvino Hezekia mambo weJudha akatuma shoko kuna mambo weAsiriya paRakishi, akati, Ndatadza, dzokai henyu mubve kwandiri; zvose zvamunoreva kwandiri ndichazviripa. Ipapo mambo weAsiriya akaripisa Hezekia mambo weJudha matarenda ana mazana matatu esirivha namatarenda ana makumi matatu endarama.
\v 15 Hezekia akamupa sirivha yose yakange iri mumba maJehovha, napafuma yeimba yamambo.
\v 16 Nenguva iyo Hezekia wakabvisa ndarama pamikova yeimba yaJehovha, napambiru dzakange dzafukidzwa nayo naHezekia mambo waJudha, akaipa mambo weAsiriya.
\v 17 Zvino mambo weAsiriya akatuma mukuru wehondo, nomukuru wamachinda, nomukuru wavatariri vabve Rakishi nehondo huru vaende kuna Hezekia paJerusarema. Ivo vakaenda, vakasvika Jerusarema. Zvino vakati vasvika, vakamira pamugero wedziva rokumusoro, riri panzira huru inoenda kumunda womusuki.
\v 18 Zvino vakati vadana mambo, Eriakimu mwanakomana waHirikia, waichengeta imba, naShebhana munyori, naJoa mwanakomana waAsafi sahwira, va kabudira kwavari.
\v 19 Zvino mukuru wavatariri akati kwavari, Zvino imwi muti kuna Hezekia, Zvanzi namambo mukuru, mambo weAsiriya, chaunovimba nacho chinyi?
\v 20 Iwe unoti (asi mashoko omuromo hawo), mano nesimba zvokurwa nazvo zviripo hazvo. Zvino unovimba naniko, zvawandimukira ini?
\v 21 Tarira zvino, unovimba nomudonzvo worutsanga urwu rwakapwanyika, Egipita, runoti kana munhu akasendama kwaruri, ruchapinda muruoko rwake, rukamubaya; ndizvo zvakaita Farao mambo weEgipita kuna vose vanovimba naye.
\v 22 Asi kana ukati kwandiri, Tinovimba naJehovha Mwari wedu, ko haasi iye wakabvisirwa matunhu akakwirira nearitari dzake naHezekia, akati kuna Judha naJerusarema, Munofanira kunamata pamberi pearitari iri paJerusarema, here?
\p
\v 23 Naizvozvo zvino, chipikiranai henyu natenzi wangu mambo weAsiriya, ndikupe mabhiza ane zviuru zviviri, kana iwe ukagona kuisa vatasvi pamusoro pawo.
\p
\v 24 Ungagona sei kukunda mukuru umwe  kuna vaduku vavaranda vatenzi vangu, kana ukavimba naEgipita kuti upiwe ngoro namabhiza navo?
\v 25 Ini ndauya kuzorwa nenzvimbo iyi kuti ndiiparadze ndisina Jehovha here? Ndiye Jehovha wakati kwandiri, Enda undorwa nenyika iyo, uiparadze.
\v 26 Ipapo Eriakimu mwanakomana waHirikia, naShebhana, naJoa vakati kumukuru wavatariri, Tinokumbira kuti mutaure henyu navaranda venyu norurimi rwechiAramaia, nekuti tinochinzwisisa; murege henyu kutaura nesu norurimi rwavaJudha, vanhu vose vari parusvingo vazvinzwe.
\p
\v 27 Asi mukuru wavatariri wakati kwaari, Tenzi wangu wakandituma kuna tenzi wako nokwauri here, kuti nditaure mashoko awa? Haana kundituma here kuvanhu vagere pamusoro porusvingo, kuti vadye ndove yavo nemvura yavo pamwechete nemi?
\p
\v 28 Ipapo mukuru wavatariri akamira, akadanidzira nenzwi guru norurimi rwavaJudha, akataura achiti, inzwai shoko ramambo mukuru, iye mambo weAsiriya.
\v 29 Zvanzi namambo, Hezekia ngaarege kukunyengerai; nekuti haagoni kukurwirai pamaoko ake;
\v 30 Hezekia ngaarege kukuvimbisai naJehovha, achiti Jehovha uchatirwira zvirokwazvo, uye kuti guta iri haringaiswi mumaoko amambo weAsiriya.
\v 31 Musateerera Hezekia, nekuti zvanzi namambo weAsiriya, Yananai neni, mubudirei kwandiri, mudye umwe  neumwe   muzambiringa wake, umwe  neumwe   muwonde wake, umwe  neumwe   mvura yetsime rake;
\v 32 kusvikira ini ndauya ndikutorei, ndikuisei kunyika yakafanana neyenyu, nyika ine zviyo newaini, nyika ine chingwa neminda yemizambiringa, nyika inamafuta emiorivhi nouchi, murarame, murege kufa, regai kuteerera Hezekia, kana achikugombedzerai achiti, Jehovha uchatirwira.
\p
\v 33 Ko umwe  wavamwari vendudzi wakatomborwira nyika yake paruoko rwamambo weAsiriya here?
\v 34 Vamwari veHamati neAripadhi varipi? Vamwari veSefarivhaimi, neHena, neIvha varipi vakarwira Samaria paruoko rwangu here?
\v 35 Ndavapiko pakati pavamwari vose venyika vakarwira nyika yavo paruoko rwangu, zvamunoti Jehovha ucharwira Jerusarema paruoko rwangu?
\p
\v 36 Asi vanhu vakaramba vanyerere, havana kumupindura shoko rimwe, nekuti murairo wamambo wakange uchiti, Regai kumupindura.
\v 37 Zvino Eriakimu mwanakomana waHirikia, waitarira imba, naShebha munyori, naJoa, mwanakomana waAsafi sahwira, vakaenda kuna Hezekia, nguwo dzavo dzabvarurwa, vakamuudza mashoko omukuru wavatariri.
